{"id":4247,"date":"2025-06-16T16:53:25","date_gmt":"2025-06-16T09:53:25","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4247"},"modified":"2025-06-16T16:53:25","modified_gmt":"2025-06-16T09:53:25","slug":"kem-chong-nang-la-gi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/kem-chong-nang-la-gi\/","title":{"rendered":"Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng l\u00e0 g\u00ec? V\u00ec sao s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><b><i>Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> m\u00e0 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 \u201cl\u00e1 ch\u1eafn\u201d kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a l\u00e0n da, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf qu\u1ed1c gia c\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 tia UV cao nh\u01b0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam? \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ai quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1ec1n c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n \u2013 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn. B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft sau \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n n\u1eafm b\u1eaft to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng \u2013 t\u1eeb th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n, c\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng cho \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1eb9o ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.\u00a0<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"kem-chong-nang-la-gi\"><\/span><b>Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u00f3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, <\/span><b>kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">? \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ee9c x\u1ea1 m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi l\u00ean da, th\u00f4ng qua vi\u1ec7c h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5, ph\u00e2n t\u00e1n ho\u1eb7c ph\u1ea3n chi\u1ebfu c\u00e1c tia c\u1ef1c t\u00edm \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 tia UVA v\u00e0 UVB. Nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i tia n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y n\u00ean s\u1ea1m m\u00e0u, n\u00e1m da, n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 ung th\u01b0 da n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ly-do-ban-nen-dung-kem-chong-nang-moi-ngay\"><\/span><b>L\u00fd do b\u1ea1n n\u00ean d\u00f9ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tia UV kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n khi tr\u1eddi n\u1eafng g\u1eaft m\u00e0 v\u1eabn t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi r\u00e2m m\u00e1t ho\u1eb7c ng\u1ed3i trong nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n c\u1eeda s\u1ed5. Do \u0111\u00f3, l\u00e0n da c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ngay c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng ra ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi. S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n gi\u00fap:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4248\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4248\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4248\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/72-1.webp\" alt=\"L\u00fd do b\u1ea1n n\u00ean d\u00f9ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/72-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/72-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/72-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/72-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4248\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">L\u00fd do b\u1ea1n n\u00ean d\u00f9ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba ch\u00e1y n\u1eafng, th\u00e2m s\u1ea1m v\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e3o h\u00f3a s\u1edbm do \u00e1nh n\u1eafng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh v\u1ec1 da li\u1ec5u do b\u1ee9c x\u1ea1 m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi g\u00e2y ra.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, nh\u1eefng ai c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, \u0111ang \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng thu\u1ed1c b\u00f4i ngo\u00e0i da hay t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da c\u00e0ng c\u1ea7n thoa kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng theo \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thoi-diem-nao-can-boi-kem-chong-nang\"><\/span><b>Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o c\u1ea7n b\u00f4i kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tia c\u1ef1c t\u00edm c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xuy\u00ean qua c\u1eeda k\u00ednh, m\u00e2y v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o m\u1ecfng. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean thoa kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng m\u1ed7i s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u1edbi, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi ch\u1ec9 ng\u1ed3i v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c trong nh\u00e0.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ai th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh m\u00e1y t\u00ednh, \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i hay \u0111\u00e8n LED, th\u00ec \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng xanh (HEV) c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u201cth\u1ee7 ph\u1ea1m\u201d g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i cho l\u00e0n da kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng trong nh\u00e0.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nhung-chi-so-can-luu-y-khi-chon-kem-chong-nang\"><\/span><b>Nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd khi ch\u1ecdn kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4249\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4249\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4249\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/72-2.webp\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd khi ch\u1ecdn kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/72-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/72-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/72-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/72-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4249\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd khi ch\u1ecdn kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h4><b>\u25b8 SPF \u2013 Sun Protection Factor<\/b><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i tia UVB. SPF 30 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kho\u1ea3ng 5 ti\u1ebfng trong \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1t 50\u201370% do m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i, kh\u00f3i b\u1ee5i, ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac n\u01b0\u1edbc. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n n\u1eafng g\u1eaft ho\u1eb7c \u0111i bi\u1ec3n, n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn SPF t\u1eeb 50 tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4><b>\u25b8 PA \u2013 Protection Grade of UVA<\/b><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi tia UVA. PA+ b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, PA++ cho hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 trung b\u00ecnh, PA+++ v\u00e0 PA++++ d\u00e0nh cho nhu c\u1ea7u cao, th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 da d\u1ec5 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac n\u1eafng m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"kem-chong-nang-pho-rong-la-gi\"><\/span><b>Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef &#8220;ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng&#8221; (Broad Spectrum) tr\u00ean bao b\u00ec cho bi\u1ebft s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi <\/span><b>c\u1ea3 UVA v\u00e0 UVB<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u2013 hai lo\u1ea1i tia nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t trong \u00e1nh n\u1eafng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea7n \u01b0u ti\u00ean n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cao.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"phan-loai-kem-chong-nang-tren-thi-truong\"><\/span><b>Ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ef1a v\u00e0o k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng hi\u1ec7n nay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea1ng:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4250\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4250\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4250\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/72-3.webp\" alt=\"Ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/72-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/72-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/72-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/72-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4250\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ea1ng l\u0103n: Ti\u1ec7n d\u1ee5ng, nh\u1ecf g\u1ecdn, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho v\u00f9ng da nh\u1ecf v\u00e0 da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ea1ng x\u1ecbt: Th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9ng, d\u1ec5 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7n x\u1ecbt \u0111\u1ec1u tay \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf s\u00f3t v\u00f9ng da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ea1ng gel: M\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9, m\u00e1t l\u1ea1nh, th\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi da d\u1ea7u nh\u01b0ng d\u1ec5 tr\u00f4i khi g\u1eb7p n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ea1ng s\u1eefa (emulsion): L\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9, d\u1ec5 th\u1ea5m, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho l\u00e0n da d\u1ec5 b\u00ed t\u1eafc ho\u1eb7c nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ea1ng kem (cream): K\u1ebft c\u1ea5u \u0111\u1eb7c h\u01a1n, d\u1ec5 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t li\u1ec1u l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, l\u00e0 d\u1ea1ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t cho m\u1ecdi lo\u1ea1i da.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"mot-vai-luu-y-khi-su-dung-kem-chong-nang\"><\/span><b>M\u1ed9t v\u00e0i l\u01b0u \u00fd khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Thoa tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ra n\u1eafng \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 20\u201330 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m k\u1ecbp ph\u00e1t huy t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u00f4i l\u1ea1i sau m\u1ed7i 2\u20134 ti\u1ebfng, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u1ed5 m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i nhi\u1ec1u ho\u1eb7c b\u01a1i l\u1ed9i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ee7 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u2013 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng 1-2g cho to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 khu\u00f4n m\u1eb7t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch \u2013 tr\u00e1nh \u00e1nh n\u1eafng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, n\u01a1i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 cao.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u1ebb em d\u01b0\u1edbi 6 th\u00e1ng ho\u1eb7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 b\u1ec7nh da li\u1ec5u c\u1ea7n h\u1ecfi \u00fd ki\u1ebfn b\u00e1c s\u0129 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u00f9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f2n b\u0103n kho\u0103n <\/span><b>kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng l\u00e0 g\u00ec, t<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">h\u00ec c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0: m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu cho l\u00e0n da m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u1eef cho da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y c\u00f2n g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 ung th\u01b0 da. H\u00e3y b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00f3i quen s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ngay t\u1eeb h\u00f4m nay \u2013 v\u00ec l\u00e0n da \u0111\u1eb9p l\u00e0 l\u00e0n da \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch!<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft sau \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n n\u1eafm b\u1eaft to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng \u2013 t\u1eeb th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n, c\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng cho \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1eb9o ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4251,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4247","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4247","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4247"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4247\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4252,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4247\/revisions\/4252"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[